gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Celtics 108, Raptors 105
gameRecap.excerpt: The Celtics defeated the Raptors, 108-105. Jaylen Brown recorded 23 points, 4 assists, and 3 rebounds for the Celtics, while Jayson Tatum added 17 points and 7 rebounds in the victory. Dennis Schroder tallied 23 points, 7 rebounds, and 6 assists for the Raptors in the losing effort. The Celtics improve to 2-0 in East Group C play, and 10-2 in the regular season, while the Raptors fall to 0-1 in East Group C play, and 5-7 in the regular season.
